1. OpenCV C++编译环境步骤
   参考 https://docs.opencv.org/4.5.0/d7/d9f/tutorial_linux_install.html

2. Sample代码
   参考 resize.cpp
   参考 https://qiita.com/yoyoyoyoyo/items/aada199371f6802bb887
   参考 https://docs.opencv.org/3.4/d4/da8/group__imgcodecs.html

3. 编译步骤
   g++ `pkg-config --cflags opencv4` -o resize resize.cpp `pkg-config --libs opencv4`
   g++ `pkg-config --cflags opencv` -o resize-4x4-A3 resize-4x4-A3.cpp -lopencv_core -lopencv_imgcodecs -lopencv_imgproc

4. 运行环境准备(??)
   sudo apt install opencv
   sudo apt install libopencv-dev

5. 运行app
   ./resize